On the Gobierno panel the meters settle to the new reign: cooptación moderate and calculating, represión lowered to the technocratic setting — selective, quieter, no less final for the selected. Between those needles, and behind Reyes Heroles' spectacles, sits the next act of this long game: the registry. Everything until now was the price of the ticket. The theater is about to open its doors.
